POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (15): GLOBAL ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS CIRCULATING VACCINE-DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2 (DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF CONGO, NIGERIA, YEMEN), ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLE (EGYPT), COMMENT ON CVDPV3 AND OPV3
